text.tspan: I am currently a fourth-year student at UW-Eau Claire, Majoring in
Business Administration, and Minoring in Multimedia
Communication, with an expected graduation date of May 2025. I am
currently working as a Team Lead at Menards Distribution Center. My
prior work experience consists of mainly retail and guest service
positions. I would like to find a job more focused on
creativity/design/marketing, to use and further my experience with
Its not often I find much time outside of school and work, but when I
do, Im usually at the gym, or working on some kind of personal
project. I have always had a passion towards cars, specificially older
american muscle cars, but I find appreciation in all kinds.
